    {
      "block_id": "doxlgu9ZV79vOn9G3yuHCtXAEed",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "说句大实话，刚看了广大网友们对 OpenClaw 的各种玩法后，我是不太感冒的。因为我对一个 24小时 On Call 的“办公助手”其实并没有太大刚需。出于对这个风头正盛项目的技术好奇，我还是仔细研究了一下它的原理。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgzkwYpbnEJSc15CgSfDSHRh",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "但当我深入研究了它的三大核心机制后，我被深深震撼了：",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgoLi7RPNAh462taB6JylPAg",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "心跳机制 (Heartbeat)",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：它不仅是定时的“闹钟”，而是让 Agent 每隔几分钟主动“醒来”，读取当前的状态和备忘录。这打破了传统自动化只能“坐等触发”的被动局面，实现了真正的",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "主动感知",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgbgmAEc2KB3fWt9nSXdW3Yb",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "永久记忆 (Memory)",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：OpenClaw 不止有临时的上下文，更有一套完整的 Markdown 文件系统（如 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "MEMORY.md",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": true,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "）。它把用户的对话、习惯甚至当时的情绪都记录下来，沉淀为长期记忆。这意味着 AI 不再是金鱼记忆，而是能",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "越用越懂你的老友",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgPmNHOXXnYFtRtAp7VNVDbf",
      "block_type": 13,
      "block_type_name": "ordered",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "自我迭代 (Self-Iteration)",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：这是最“炸裂”的一点。Agent 被授权可以修改自己的提示词和任务列表。当它发现你的新习惯时，它能自己改写运行逻辑来适应你。这不是人工配置，这是",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "系统的自我进化",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
