      "block_type": 12,
      "block_type_name": "bullet",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "现实",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "：今天你失恋了，或者刚从医院回来，只想在黑暗里静静。但自动化 ",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "不懂空气",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "，它只会像个没眼力见的傻子一样，立刻把家里搞得跟夜店一样热闹。你不得不手动去关掉那些“为了便利”而设置的开关。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
